high_descs: Go to the right sink
Pick up the knife
Go to the microwave
Cut the potato in the microwave
Look down at the sink
Put the knife in the microwave
Look down at the sink
Take a potato slice out of the microwave
Go to the left sink
Wash the potato in the left sink
Go to the white table
Put the potato slice on the table
anns.task_desc: Put a washed potato slice on the white table

high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room to face the right side of the sink.
Pick up the knife on the edge of the sink.
Take a step to the left and look up to face the microwave.
Cut the potato in the microwave into slices.
Step back and look up to face the microwave.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Step back and look up to face the microwave.
Pick up a slice of potato from in the microwave.
Take a step to the left to face the left side of the sink.
Wash the potato slice in the sink and then remove it.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the white table.
Place the piece of potato on the edge of the white table.
anns.task_desc: To wash a piece of potato and place it on the white table.

high_descs: Turn right, move to the counter in front of the large sink.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Move to in front of the microwave.
Slice the potato in the microwave.
Move to in front of the microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Move to in front of the microwave.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn left, move to the counter near the small sink.
Put the potato slice in the sink, rinse it, pick it back up.
Turn right, move to the table near the stool.
Put the potato slice on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed slice of potato on the table.
